This will be a camera tracker, that will use GFS to hoist a camera towards the target

Features:
Be able to use any form of camera configuration
Automatically locate any existing version of GFS on the grid for ease of use
Be easily toggalable and quickly changeable

Minor Features:
#Configurable camera spin speed

Progress:
#Automatic connection to GFS to collect its fire control information
#Get the turret to move to its target
#Get the turret to move ACCURATELY to allow for tracking of moving targets, most likely with PID style movement controls
